file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: A linting bug
  version: 1.0.0
  contact:
    name: vk342
    email: vk342@example.com
    url: https://example.com
tags:
  - name: transactions
    description: Endpoints related to transactions
paths:
  /transaction/{transactionId}:
    parameters:
    - $ref: '#/components/parameters/transactionIdParam'
    put:
      operationId: putTransaction
      description: Update a transaction...
      tags:
        - transactions
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              #type: object
              properties:
                txnId:
                  type: string
                  description: Unique transactionID.
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Created
components:
  parameters:
    transactionIdParam:
      name: transactionId
      in: path
      required: true
      description: An ID for the transaction
      schema:
        type: string
